[font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][color=#ffffff]This mod puts base washing statics into Skyrim world.From place to place you can stumble upon wash things.[/color]
[color=#ffffff]Wash things are placed on 14 different Locations :[/color]

[color=#000000]Whiterun :[/color][color=#ffffff]Ysolda House,Breezehome And Pelagia Farm[/color]
[color=#000000]Falkreath: [/color][/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][color=#ffffff]Corpselight Farm[/color]
[color=#000000]Morthal : [/color][/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][color=#ffffff]next to sawmill[/color]
[color=#ffffff]At the entrance of Markarth[/color]
[color=#000000]Solitude :[/color][/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][color=#ffffff]Katla's Farm and Solitude Sawmill[/color]
[color=#000000]and also :[/color]
[color=#ffffff]Sarethi Farm[/color]
[color=#ffffff]Riverwood [/color]
[color=#ffffff]Goldenglow Estate[/color]
